storyInfo: Eager to get the medicine off his hands, the Capit√°n instead draws the attention of Team Rainbow. Tequila also tracks down the delivery. Going after the same thing, the two sides almost come to blows.

attributes.content: The meds are in the underground warehouse, sir.
attributes.name: Commanding Officer

attributes.content: As you instructed, we imitated them, set up a bomb, caused a little bit of chaos, and got the stuff.
attributes.name: Commanding Officer

attributes.content: Good...
attributes.name: Mateo

attributes.content: You don't look happy, sir.
attributes.name: Commanding Officer

attributes.content: We need to get rid of the stuff... It's hard to not leave a trail, even if we change the packaging and sell it on the black market.
attributes.name: Mateo

attributes.content: You think it'll get tracked down?
attributes.name: Commanding Officer

attributes.content: I got word that Rhodes Island sent someone with an... atypical background to make the delivery.
attributes.name: Mateo

attributes.content: I noticed. The man looked familiar...
attributes.name: Commanding Officer

attributes.content: But old Pancho is in jail, and his people are scattered. Just being his son won't carry much influence.
attributes.name: Commanding Officer

attributes.content: Not necessarily. Someone from the city council let slip that Candela is looking for a successor, and the kid is a candidate.
attributes.name: Mateo

attributes.content: But I thought Pancho and Candela...
attributes.name: Commanding Officer

attributes.content: Candela cares more about ability than a personal grudge.
attributes.name: Mateo

attributes.content: What can we do?
attributes.name: Commanding Officer

attributes.content: Reynell's secretary shared some resources with us the last time he came by.
attributes.name: Mateo

attributes.content: Yes... a few shops and warehouses.
attributes.name: Commanding Officer

attributes.content: Wasn't there a warehouse that belonged to a pharmaceutical company?
attributes.name: Mateo

attributes.content: Yes.
attributes.name: Commanding Officer

attributes.content: One box of meds more or less won't catch their attention.
attributes.name: Mateo

attributes.content: You mean, pin it on Reynell?
attributes.name: Commanding Officer

attributes.content: That's not how I would put it. They came asking for our help. It's only natural that we asked for something in return.
attributes.name: Mateo

attributes.content: Apologies for keeping you waiting, Se√±or Ernesto.
attributes.name: Mayor's Bodyguard

attributes.content: No problemo, I just got here.
attributes.name: Tequila

attributes.content: Excuse me, one...
attributes.name: Mayor's Bodyguard

attributes.content: I got your drink, Se√±or Burke. A double, right?
attributes.name: Tequila

attributes.content: I'm glad you still remember what I like, after so much time away.
attributes.name: Mayor's Bodyguard

attributes.content: Our time together was much longer.
attributes.name: Tequila

attributes.content: Here's your coffee.
attributes.name: Waiter

attributes.content: Thanks. Mm... everything is just right.
attributes.name: Mayor's Bodyguard

attributes.content: After you left, there was no one who could take care of things like you could. Young people these days...
attributes.name: Mayor's Bodyguard

attributes.content: Have patience. You can change quickly in an environment like that.
attributes.name: Tequila

attributes.content: By the way, Lady Candela wanted me to give you this document.
attributes.name: Mayor's Bodyguard

attributes.content: Document? Does she want me to do something for her?
attributes.name: Tequila

attributes.content: No, it's what you're looking for.
attributes.name: Mayor's Bodyguard

attributes.content: I haven't even said why I'm here today.
attributes.name: Tequila

attributes.content: Lady Candela knows the exact moment that you entered Dossoles. She knows that your shipment was stolen, and that you're anxious to get it back.
attributes.name: Mayor's Bodyguard

attributes.content: This is a record of all unusual traffic and cargo movement, including locations and persons involved.
attributes.name: Mayor's Bodyguard

attributes.content: I don't know how I can thank her.
attributes.name: Tequila

attributes.content: No need for thanks, just don't forget us.
attributes.name: Mayor's Bodyguard

attributes.content: *cough* *cough*...
attributes.name: Ela

attributes.content: There's more dust here than cargo.
attributes.name: Fuze

attributes.content: What's your mission, Ela?
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: The stuff here has been stuck in the warehouse for the past six months, with only a single watchman keeping an eye on it.
attributes.name: Ela

attributes.content: That's like an invitation for people to help themselves.
attributes.name: Doc

attributes.content: Yes, Mi≈Çosz says there are reports of stolen goods every day.
attributes.name: Ela

attributes.content: Are we tracking down where they went?
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: No, it's normal for stuff to go out, but yesterday the watchman got a call to expect a delivery of medicine.
attributes.name: Ela

attributes.content: Mi≈Çosz is suspicious and wants us to investigate.
attributes.name: Ela

attributes.content: Hostile intent?
attributes.name: Fuze

attributes.content: Hard to say. I don't know what they would want with a warehouse like this.
attributes.name: Doc

attributes.content: Maybe Mi≈Çosz just wanted an excuse to get you and Shuhrat out of the way now that he finally has time to get something done with Reynell.
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: All he needs to do is ask, and I won't go within a kilometer of either of them.
attributes.name: Ela

attributes.content: You really don't like him, do you?
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: I just don't like having to watch him play golf on the balcony every day.
attributes.name: Ela

attributes.content: At least he kept his promise to behave.
attributes.name: Fuze

attributes.content: This is where the clues from the document lead, but...
attributes.name: Tequila

attributes.content: But it's just an old run-down warehouse.
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: There's a shipment of medicine coming to the warehouse in a bit. Let's see if it's the one we're looking for.
attributes.name: Tequila

attributes.content: Only one watchman at the warehouse. No threat.
attributes.name: Tequila

attributes.content: Once the truck comes in, Tecno is going to turn off the security systems and let us go in to check it out.
attributes.name: Tequila

attributes.content: Well, we still have to wait...
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: (Yawns)
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: *yawn* Sleepy...
attributes.name: Warehouse Watchman

attributes.content: When is that shipment going to arrive?
attributes.name: Warehouse Watchman

attributes.content: I can't believe they're actually sending someone to inspect it. What for? The weather is so good, I just want to find a beach to lie down on, have a cup of coffee, listen to a song or two.
attributes.name: Warehouse Watchman

attributes.content: Dancing a soundless tango at night‚ô™
attributes.name: Warehouse Watchman

attributes.content: Where's the CD? Ah.
attributes.name: Warehouse Watchman

attributes.content: Dancing a soundless tango at night‚ô™
attributes.name: Sound from Headphones

attributes.content: I can't see your face, only the warmth of your hand‚ô™
attributes.name: Sound from Headphones

attributes.content: Now this is life.
attributes.name: Warehouse Watchman

attributes.content: (He's not even trying...)
attributes.name: Tecno

attributes.content: (If you want to sleep so badly, I'll lend you a hand.)
attributes.name: Tecno

attributes.content: Oomph...
attributes.name: Warehouse Watchman

attributes.content: That was easy. Let's see, where are the controls?
attributes.name: Tecno

attributes.content: I thought there was just one manager. Why are there four people here? Who are they?
attributes.name: Tecno

attributes.content: The security systems are down. I have good news and bad news. The good news is that we know those meds are the ones we're looking for.
attributes.name: Tecno

attributes.content: The bad news is that Reynell's bodyguards are here. Four of them, all in the warehouse.
attributes.name: Tecno

attributes.content: I thought nobody ever came here.
attributes.name: Tequila

attributes.content: Well, we've got a disadvantage in numbers... can you cut the lights, Tecno? Arleta and I might be able to sneak in under the cover of darkness.
attributes.name: Tequila

attributes.content: Sure, I could try...
attributes.name: Tecno

attributes.content: It's off.
attributes.name: Tecno

attributes.content: Alright, we're moving.
attributes.name: Tequila

attributes.content: Well, this guy knows how to live alright. Music and coffee... is that this year's crop?
attributes.name: Tecno

attributes.content: (Sniffs)
attributes.name: Tecno
Tecno
attributes.content: It smells good‚Ä¶

attributes.name: Tecno
attributes.content: Ouch! Too hot!
Shoot, spilled it all over the keyboard.
attributes.name: Tecno

attributes.content: Where's a napkin when you need it?!
attributes.name: Tecno

attributes.content: She stops at the sound of springs pushing a plastic cover open.
She hastily lifts her arm and sees an indicating light glowing green next to the keyboard. Below it is a tag that reads‚Äî
'Broadcasting.'
When is it coming?
attributes.name: Ela

attributes.content: Don't worry, we have time.
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: I guess that's normal for an old warehouse like this.
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: Dancing a soundless tango at night‚ô™
attributes.name: Sound from Loudspeakers

attributes.content: I can't see your face, only the warmth of your hand‚ô™
attributes.name: Sound from Loudspeakers

attributes.content: Fuze, check out the control room.
attributes.name: Ela

attributes.content: In a dark corner‚ô™
attributes.name: Sound from Loudspeakers

attributes.content: You step on my toes, but I'm head over heels‚ô™
attributes.name: Sound from Loudspeakers

attributes.content: Shouldn't have drank that stupid cup of coffee!
attributes.name: Tecno

attributes.content: (Someone's coming...)
attributes.name: Tecno

attributes.content: (I need to hide.)
attributes.name: Tecno

attributes.content: Excuse me?
attributes.name: Fuze

attributes.content: The watchman has been knocked out. There are signs of sabotage in the security and lighting systems.
attributes.name: Fuze

attributes.content: Someone has infiltrated the warehouse.
attributes.name: Fuze

attributes.content: They spilled coffee and pressed the wrong button... not a professional, from the looks of it.
attributes.name: Fuze

attributes.content: I'll try to get the lights back up.
attributes.name: Fuze

attributes.content: (Looks like Ernesto isn't in yet. Got to put you to sleep too then, big guy.)
attributes.name: Tecno

attributes.content: Hm?
attributes.name: Fuze

attributes.content: (Oh, he's fast!)
attributes.name: Tecno

attributes.content: A kid?
attributes.name: Fuze

attributes.content: Fuze is shocked by the figure leaping out of the darkness, not just because of her small size, but also because her punch was so fast that it was all he could do to block it.
He grabs the girl's wrist after a few exchanges and attempts to restrain her, but quickly realizes that things will not be so easy.
Not so fast!
attributes.name: Tecno

attributes.content: What?! This kid's stronger than a grown man!
attributes.name: Fuze

attributes.content: I'm not a kid!
attributes.name: Tecno

attributes.content: The girl struggles free of Fuze's grasp and stomps on his toes.
Before he has a chance to feel the pain, the girl launches a spinning kick to his face.
Oof‚Äî
attributes.name: Fuze

attributes.content: Walking on the streets, we let each other's hands go‚ô™
attributes.name: Sound from Loudspeakers

attributes.content: Far away you go, never seen again‚ô™
attributes.name: Sound from Loudspeakers

attributes.content: I'm left alone, searching in the dark‚ô™
attributes.name: Sound from Loudspeakers

attributes.content: Oh, the silent, unfinished tango‚ô™
attributes.name: Sound from Loudspeakers

attributes.content: (Whisper) Stay close.
attributes.name: Tequila

attributes.content: (Whisper) Alright.
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: The pair sneak forward silently along the wall, not realizing that another group is doing the same a short distance away.
(Whisper) Fuze?! He's not answering.
attributes.name: Ela

attributes.content: (Whisper) Should we look for him?
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: (Whisper) No, I'll go. You wait here for the truck. There must be more than one infiltrator.
attributes.name: Ela

attributes.content: (Whisper) Be aware that we can't use lights if someone is lying in wait. We'd be sitting ducks.
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: (Whisper) Do you want to use my night vision goggles?
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: (Whisper) You hold on to it. I'll be careful.
attributes.name: Ela

attributes.content: Ela crouches down, clutching her gun, feeling her way in the darkness.
(Damn... where did Arleta go? I told her to stay close.)
attributes.name: Tequila

attributes.content: (It's just so hard to do anything in the dark.)
attributes.name: Tequila

attributes.content: (Was it this way? I might have taken a wrong turn. There shouldn't be another corner.)
attributes.name: Tequila

attributes.content: So many times, brushing past each other‚ô™
attributes.name: Sound from Loudspeakers

attributes.content: (There shouldn't have been a corner here! Not this way!)
attributes.name: Ela

attributes.content: So much searching, so much lost‚ô™
attributes.name: Sound from Loudspeakers

attributes.content: Maybe we'll see each other again, at the next corner‚ô™
attributes.name: Sound from Loudspeakers

attributes.content: (I hope not.)
attributes.name: Ela & Tequila

attributes.content: (Whisper) Ernesto?
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: (Uh oh, I lost him.)
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: Who's there?!
attributes.name: Catapult

attributes.content: (Whisper) Did the girl not realize she was walking in circles around the same wall?
attributes.name: Doc

attributes.content: (Whisper) Not everyone has night vision. Say, I think I've seen her before.
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: (Whisper) She was in that art community yesterday... should we leave her here?
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: (Whisper) I think her friends will come for her. I'll wait.
attributes.name: Doc

attributes.content: (Whisper) Alright, I'll look elsewhere.
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: (Mm... he's heavy.)
attributes.name: Tecno

attributes.content: (I should have stuffed you in the cupboard with the other poor bastard.)
attributes.name: Tecno

attributes.content: (Why would people from that neighborhood be here? This doesn't make sense.)
attributes.name: Doc

attributes.content: (What's that noise?)
attributes.name: Doc

attributes.content: (Hm?)
attributes.name: Doc

attributes.content: Doc holds his breath and reaches for his weapon. Auditory senses are sharpened in darkness. The dragging sound grows ever closer.
So many times, brushing past each other‚ô™
attributes.name: Sound from Loudspeakers

attributes.content: So much searching, so much lost‚ô™
attributes.name: Sound from Loudspeakers

attributes.content: Maybe we'll see each other again, at the next corner‚ô™
attributes.name: Sound from Loudspeakers

attributes.content: ‚Äî!
attributes.name: Tecno & Doc

attributes.content: Freeze!
attributes.name: Tecno & Doc

attributes.content: Their surprised exclamations send the warehouse into a frenzy.
Doc?!
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: Gustave?!
attributes.name: Ela

attributes.content: Tecno?!
attributes.name: Tequila

attributes.content: Well, you can blame your bad luck!
attributes.name: Tecno

attributes.content: What is that?
attributes.name: Ela

attributes.content: Arts flash! Get to cover, Ela!
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: Wait, Tecno, don't do it here‚Äî
attributes.name: Tequila

attributes.content: No wrong moves, girl! I've got your friend here!
attributes.name: Doc

attributes.content: Oh no, they've got Arleta!
attributes.name: Tequila

attributes.content: Hmph, we have a hostage too.
attributes.name: Tecno

attributes.content: Shuhrat!
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: The only light in the darkness is from Tecno's Arts, not bright enough to illuminate the whole warehouse, but just enough for everyone to see each other's faces.
Gazes cross and scan around, reading the same thing on the assembled faces‚Äî
(Whisper) Well, this is awkward... how did we end up here?
attributes.name: Iana

attributes.content: Maybe we can exchange hostages and each go our own way?
attributes.name: Tequila

attributes.content: Wait!
attributes.name: Tecno & Ela

attributes.content: What are you doing here?
attributes.name: Tecno

attributes.content: We have to find out who's been using this warehouse for smuggling. What about you, girl?
attributes.name: Ela

attributes.content: Looking for the meds we lost.
attributes.name: Tecno

attributes.content: We've already said we didn't steal the meds.
attributes.name: Doc

attributes.content: Really? Then what are you doing here?
attributes.name: Tequila

attributes.content: I told you, we're trying to find out who's smuggling stuff into this warehouse. What about you?
attributes.name: Ela

attributes.content: I said, this is where our meds are!
attributes.name: Tequila

attributes.content: You people are just impossible!
attributes.name: Ela

attributes.content: Hey, anybody home? Your stuff's here!
Man, all the way out in the middle of nowhere...
So... if we all want to know what's up with that shipment of meds, why don't we ask the guy who's delivering it?
attributes.name: Tequila
